ISLAMABAD, Oct 29 (APP): Group Chief Executive Attock Group of Companies Shoaib Anwar Malik called on Prime Minister Shehbaz Sharif here on Saturday and presented him a cheque of Rs 100 million.
He also gave one-day salary cheque of Rs 7.39 million from employees of Attock Group.The amount was given from all companies of the Attock Group for the Prime Ministerâ€™s Flood Relief Fund on the appeal of Prime Minister Shehbaz Sharif for the flood affectees.
